reviewText: Arrived on time and my son loves it. (He's a collector.) Thanks!
My son loves it, so that is all that matters, but it is a SHORT DVD compared to what I expected. Cute, great kids movie.

I am confused about the Amazon description. Would anyone who owns one or has seen one please tell me exactly how many episodes
are on this and how many minutes are on this? I need to know before I buy. The Amazon description says 30 minutes.

I really appreciate you having these DVD's.  I have a 6 year old grandson who just recently saw a rugrat show on TV.  He loved it and I thought, I would get more for his enjoyment.  I am glad you had such a selection.  The delivery was accomplished quickly.  Thanks for your help and service.  Ina Holland
my child loved the dvd. He is a fan of the rugrats so i decided to get it for him.i recommend it .

What can I say I grew up watching the Rugrats I love this cartoon. I purchased every DVD and a bunch of VHS Tapes recently because my daughters (4 and 2) love it just as much as I used to, and still do. Great picture and sound. Can't be beat. Also look for Rugrats-Decade in diapers, if you like this you'll love that one as well.
Another in the series of fine Rugrats episodes. The fun keeps coming and coming and I recommend this to any Rugrat fan or newcomer to the Rugrat family.
Came early with all my other packages fantastic deal
